<br>
High Resists, 80 is minimum but 100+ is the goal.<br>
<br>
Dont worry about AC, if the dragon wants to hit you, she will.   Her 3 to 7 level advantage will prove enough that AC is not a critical factor.<br>
<br>
Bum, borrow, or buy a high level cleric to assist you.  A 57 cleric can symbol and hero your whole squad in less than 20 minutes provided you have a few people around to assist with mana.  <br>
<br>
Circle of Summer and Circle of Winter are musts.  Tossing in a few root potions to keep the tanks from running is not a bad idea either.<br>
<br>
Send one group of tanks in first to pull the dragon to the back of the lair.  Too many raids fail because Vox gets situated in the rock near the entrance.  <br>
<br>
Send all the rest of your tanks in 10 seconds after the first group.  Having tanks in reserve is just wasting damage.<br>
<br>
Debuffers go in after the tanks, cast your debuffs.  Enchanters need to start draining Vox ASAP.  If your agrso, dont do the 'Caster Dance'!  Battles are lost because one caster decides to kite Vox while 20 tanks give merry chase.<br>
<br>
When the tanks have a firm lock on the dragon and you see the life force start draining away.  Send in the casters for the final blow.<br>
 <p>Segal - 60 Cleric - Luclin <br>
Chachon - 51 Monk - Luclin <BR>
